blog.title: i don't feel great
blog.description: just a girl who writes about her feelings and every mood swing that i get

body:
23.09.2018

Okay so this may sound silly but I had the weirdest dream. I was at a table with Emma Chamberlain and Harry Styles and some other people. I was trying to not freak out and act normal and polite. Emma was really cool and agreed to take a picture with me but we didn’t do it for some reason. I asked kindly Harry if I could take a picture with him, but he wanted to write me something instead. I don’t remember exactly what but one sentence stuck with me: ‘Why do you do this to me?’. And that’s all I can remember. What did I do? When I woke up I had a strange feeling, I was craving love, a romantic love and I had a question, what is going on in artists minds sometimes?

title: Ooh Aah Vol. 1
body:
Ooh Aah Vol. 1

As I write this, I am shuddering at the thought of my looming deadlines, all the PDF’s of academic journal articles open and waiting to be read, and minimum word counts waiting to be met. Clearly, I should be writing my thesis instead of this blog post right now. Yet, here I am. Writing it. A fun fact about me is that I have zero will power!

There are a few things that I have been enjoying for…
